<section id="about">
  <div>
    <h1>Entrepreneur. Educator. Security Architect.</h1>
    <p>I am an entrepreneur and technologist with over 15 years of experience scaling enterprise software. My core expertise lies in architecting secure, identity-driven systems, with a specialized focus on Identity and Access Management (IAM), API security, OAuth, and OpenID Connect. After spending the last decade building and scaling identity platforms as an executive and founder, I am currently managing private holdings. My ongoing focus remains at the intersection of technical architecture and strategic growth, analyzing the future of AI-agent security, decentralized identity, and developer infrastructure.</p>
  </div>
</section>

